463
00:34:37,720 --> 00:34:39,120
Pýtaj sa.

464
00:34:43,150 --> 00:34:48,660
Bráško Tian Xing a Tao Le Si...

465
00:34:48,660 --> 00:34:50,920
ako je to medzi nimi teraz?

466
00:34:52,750 --> 00:34:54,500
Neviem.

467
00:34:54,500 --> 00:34:56,550
Ale podľa Tian Xingovej povahy,

